<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It seems that the Zend_Form_Element_File only works if an file is actually uploaded. If not validation of within Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract throws an exception in the -&gt;_getFiles() method, because it could not find any files related to the respective form element. The -&gt;_getFiles() method provides a third argument which could be used to block the exception. This argument however is not used by the calling -&gt;isValid() method.</p>

